<p><span class="anchor" id="p28"></span>لِسَعْيِها راضِيَةٌ <span class="c2">(٩)</span><a href="#p28" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p29"></span><span class="c2">«لِسَعْيِها»</span> جار ومجرور متعلقان بما بعدهما <span class="c2">«راضِيَةٌ»</span> خبر ثان لوجوه.<a href="#p29" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
